title: Zed's Lore
body: So I was reading Zed's lore and it seemed strangely familiar, as if I seen it in a movie one time. So I was thinking intensely for about 33 seconds trying to remember where I knew it from. After about 2 minutes of YouTube research I found this: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sHcYIhB-XAY
